{"tid":1573833,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「幫手置頂」推到929搞手、民陣、機場壓測搞手入黎！！","createTime":"2019-09-16T06:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T18:22:02.000Z","uid":218570,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"714e63e176da41494953c765bc4de926043da384","tid":1573833,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:54:44.000Z","msg":"915遊行班狗出左反對<br />\n民陣話會繼續申請928同10.1大遊行<br />\n但之前有手足吹過大雞搞929全球反共遊行<br />\n而今日我見到呂麗搖巴宣傳928會搞壓測<br />\n<br />\n所以928 929嘅活動會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">超級Full</span></span><br />\n兩日兩個遊行加壓測會分薄好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實有冇可能將兩個大遊行<span style=\"color: orange;\">合而為一</span><br />\n整個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">超級大禮</span></span>比共產黨？<br />\n<br />\n我明白928有重大意義(雨革)<br />\n但係929又會近啲国慶 加上星期日會多人啲<br />\n想各位手足幫幫手推po或者比意見<br />\n睇下點樣可以三全其美<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返兩個禮拜咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要盡快搞掂再谷恆文宣"},{"pid":"f689030e03c5605ce74cdf204f07a3aa2d70d540","tid":1573833,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBfJ3Kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBfJ3Kt.jpg&h=035c3ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qpM4horlrIe